
---

# 📦 .gitignore（Jasper + IntelliJ + Maven 完整版）

```gitignore
# ========================
# IntelliJ
# ========================
.idea/
*.iml

# ========================
# Maven
# ========================
target/
pom.xml.tag
pom.xml.releaseBackup
pom.xml.versionsBackup
pom.xml.next

# ========================
# OS
# ========================
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db

# ========================
# Logs
# ========================
*.log

# ========================
# JasperReports
# ========================
*.jasper

# ========================
# Temp / cache
# ========================
*.tmp
*.temp
*.cache

# ========================
# Output PDF (不要上傳產物)
# ========================
*.pdf
jasperResults/

# ========================
# Eclipse / Jaspersoft Studio
# ========================
.project
.classpath
.settings/

# ========================
# VSCode
# ========================
.vscode/

# ========================
# Fonts（如果你不想上傳字型）
# ========================
# src/main/resources/fonts/*.ttf
